title: _:GEM2-labelled Mito-EGFP in HeLa cells
biological_entity_description: HeLa cells expressing Mito-EGFP and genetically encoded multimeric particle (GEM) GEM2 system. Mito-EGFP specifically labels mitochondria, while the GEM2 system provides genetically encoded multimeric nanoparticles for visualization by electron microscopy.
